title: A1A Burrito Works Taco Shop
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small taco and burrito stand with well seasoned tempeh available for most entrees. Great late-night hours and right next to the public beach access. Does not clearly label vegan items. Must request removal of cheese or some sauces to make some dishes vegan.
